# SegmentedSlider 分段滑块

用于在预定义的离散选项中进行选择的分段滑块组件。

## 基础用法

### SegmentedSlider
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SegmentedSliderSegmentedSliderDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const value = ref(1)
  const segments = [
    { value: 0, label: 'Small' },
    { value: 1, label: 'Medium' },
    { value: 2, label: 'Large' },
    { value: 3, label: 'XL' },
  ]
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; width: 400px;">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.72; margin-bottom: 8px;">
          当前值: {{ value }}
        </div>
        <TxSegmentedSlider v-model="value" :segments="segments" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

